{"tid":2453011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：外交部新聞司就BBC涉華不實報道提出嚴正交涉","createTime":"2021-03-19T07:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T07:57:16.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6865d7c058a9490eb030c6f37c8bf04de61109","tid":2453011,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"外交部新聞司負責人近日就英國廣播公司(BBC)世界新聞頻道涉疆強迫勞動、中國限制新聞自由和BBC廣播四台等報道，向BBC駐京分社提出嚴正交涉，要求停止對華污蔑、抹黑、攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n新聞司負責人指出，BBC在涉華報道中，<strong>抱持強烈意識形態偏見，多次炒作涉疆、涉疫情、涉港等不實信息，甚至炮製假新聞</strong>，中國外交部及駐英國使館亦已多次向BBC總部和駐京分社提出嚴正交涉。但BBC不但未採取措施改正錯誤，近期還變本加厲，圍繞涉疆、所謂新聞自由和假信息等議題，持續對華攻擊抹黑，嚴重誤導觀眾，嚴重違背客觀、公正的新聞報道原則，影響惡劣。中方對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581487-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581487-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=01d9d262\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581487-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=528056b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581487-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"268705868b5f6473b173d244f4a6c7f17f314f14","tid":2453011,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:51:41.000Z","msg":"SO？"},{"pid":"847bd7c2f7bc87fccdff6b1ebcb478d5e278dd33","tid":2453011,"uid":363413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}